{"tid":1964260,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) [失業]我岩岩先俾公司炒左，轉頭就見果間垃圾請梗intern","createTime":"2020-04-08T16:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T06:28:17.000Z","uid":82465,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bdeeed9d55d17719b817336d2136ad065dfca06e","tid":1964260,"uid":82465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:31:37.000Z","msg":"相信唔少大學year 2同year 3都揾緊intern<br />\n<br />\n今日上Linkedin 搵工見到一堆 Placement Intern<br />\n就見果間垃圾忽然請梗intern<br />\n<br />\n今年生意唔好<br />\n有interview offer 都要特別小心<br />\n有D 公司話就話請intern<br />\n但入面分分鐘Intern係入面要做到one-man band<br />\n唔好講做嘢一個頂十個<br />\n到時份糧都唔知有冇得出添呀<br />\n好撚伏<br />\n<br />\n仲有d startup講到自己幾好幾正幾個國家都有生意<br />\n隨時連幾千蚊人工都俾唔起<br />\n<br />\n我做果間野仲要俾你地連登誤吹係黃<br />\n明明就做成班藍絲生意 執左死雞<br />\n<br />\n當你以為得食飯可以有半價 其實人工都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd37dd710e07ec8ab698fb8563a54714d0816845","tid":1964260,"uid":82465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"飲飲食食app"},{"pid":"c9f65c07a3ccb5486da1a11e2effa0a1420ebd57","tid":1964260,"uid":85118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"屌 有無咁賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55143dad914e62e069b93547164abae9ccfcf976","tid":1964260,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd37dd710e07ec8ab698fb8563a54714d0816845","tid":1964260,"uid":82465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"飲飲食食app"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:22:47.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"2323daef50618bd18457855f655ed1765c256d1a","tid":1964260,"uid":175032,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"你唔開名都比個initial黎估吓<br />\n唔知頭唔知路邊有得陪你屌啊"},{"pid":"f0ec5139af5f02cce640b6babfcb681465e20bf4","tid":1964260,"uid":82465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:2